items.title: IBM Seen as ‘Stable Compounder’ — Stifel Lifts Price Target Ahead of Q2
items.description: International Business Machines Corporation (NYSE:IBM) is one of the AI Stocks Investors Are Watching Closely. On July 16, Stifel analyst David Grossman reaffirmed a “Buy” rating for the stock and increased the price target from $290.00 to $310.00. Stifel’s rating reflects continued optimism for IBM’s projected financial performance and potential growth ahead of its second-quarter earnings […]
